          " عَلَيْكُمْ بِالْخَسِّ فَإِنَّهُ يُصَفِّي الدَّمَ ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Abu Abdullah, from his father, from one of his companions, from Abu Hafs Al Abbar, ",
            "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘it is upon you with (eating) the lettuce, for it cleans the blood’."
          ],
          "en.sarwar": [
            "1. A number of our people have narrated from Ahmad ibn abu ‘ Abd Allah from his father from certain persons of his people from abu Hafs ibn al-Abbar who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘You must eat lettuce because it cleanses blood.’” "
          ]
        }
